queryLines:
SELECT  Group_Indicator,
        Gender,
        Issue_Age_Bucket,
        Incurred_Age_Bucket,
        Issue_Year_Bucket,
        Policy_Year,
        Marital_Status,
        Premium_Class,
        Underwriting_Type,
        Coverage_Type_Bucket,
        Tax_Qualification_Status,
        Inflation_Rider,
        Rate_Increase_Flag,
        Restoration_of_Benefits,
        Region,
        CASE 
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = " < 1991" AND Policy_Year = "10-12 years" THEN "1998-2000"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = " < 1991" AND Policy_Year = "15+ years" THEN "2004-2006"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = " < 1991" AND Policy_Year = "13-15 years" THEN "2001-2003"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1991-1993" AND Policy_Year = " 7-9 years" THEN "1998-2000"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1991-1993" AND Policy_Year = "10-12 years" THEN "2001-2003"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1991-1993" AND Policy_Year = "13-15 years" THEN "2004-2006"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1991-1993" AND Policy_Year = "15+ years" THEN "2007-2009"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1994-1996" AND Policy_Year = " 4-6 years" THEN "1998-2000"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1994-1996" AND Policy_Year = " 7-9 years" THEN "2001-2003"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1994-1996" AND Policy_Year = "10-12 years" THEN "2004-2006"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1994-1996" AND Policy_Year = "13-15 years" THEN "2007-2009"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1994-1996" AND Policy_Year = "15+ years" THEN "2010-2012"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1997-1999" AND Policy_Year = " 1-3 years" THEN "1998-2000"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1997-1999" AND Policy_Year = " 4-6 years" THEN "2001-2003"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1997-1999" AND Policy_Year = " 7-9 years" THEN "2004-2006"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1997-1999" AND Policy_Year = "10-12 years" THEN "2007-2009"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1997-1999" AND Policy_Year = "13-15 years" THEN "2010-2012"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "1997-1999" AND Policy_Year = "15+ years" THEN "2013-2015"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2000-2002" AND Policy_Year = "15+ years" THEN "2016-2018"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2000-2002" AND Policy_Year = " 4-6 years" THEN "2004-2006"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2000-2002" AND Policy_Year = " 1-3 years" THEN "2001-2003"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2000-2002" AND Policy_Year = "10-12 years" THEN "2010-2012"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2000-2002" AND Policy_Year = " 7-9 years" THEN "2007-2009"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2000-2002" AND Policy_Year = "13-15 years" THEN "2013-2015"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2003-2005" AND Policy_Year = "13-15 years" THEN "2016-2018"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2003-2005" AND Policy_Year = "10-12 years" THEN "2013-2015"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2003-2005" AND Policy_Year = " 1-3 years" THEN "2004-2006"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2003-2005" AND Policy_Year = " 4-6 years" THEN "2007-2009"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2003-2005" AND Policy_Year = " 7-9 years" THEN "2010-2012"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2006-2008" AND Policy_Year = " 4-6 years" THEN "2010-2012"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2006-2008" AND Policy_Year = " 1-3 years" THEN "2007-2009"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2006-2008" AND Policy_Year = "10-12 years" THEN "2016-2018"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2006-2008" AND Policy_Year = " 7-9 years" THEN "2013-2015"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2009-2011" AND Policy_Year = " 4-6 years" THEN "2013-2015"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2009-2011" AND Policy_Year = " 1-3 years" THEN "2010-2012"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2009-2011" AND Policy_Year = " 7-9 years" THEN "2016-2018"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2012-2014" AND Policy_Year = " 1-3 years" THEN "2013-2015"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2012-2014" AND Policy_Year = " 4-6 years" THEN "2016-2018"
          WHEN Issue_Year_Bucket = "2015-2016" AND Policy_Year = " 1-3 years" THEN "2016-2018"
        END AS Calendar_Year_Bucket,
        IDENTIFIER(concat(:claim_type, '_Orig_Daily_Ben_Bucket')) AS Orig_Daily_Ben_Bucket,
        IDENTIFIER(concat(:claim_type, '_Ben_Period_Bucket')) AS Ben_Period_Bucket,
        IDENTIFIER(concat(:claim_type, '_EP_Bucket')) AS EP_Bucket,
        Active_Exposure,
        Total_Exposure,
        IDENTIFIER(concat('Count_', :claim_type)) AS Claim_Count,
        Claim_Count / Total_Exposure * 1000 AS Incidence_Rate
  FROM IDENTIFIER(concat('actuarial_app_catalog.`long_term_care`.', :table_name))
  WHERE Incurred_Age_Bucket != 'Unknown'

datasets.name: 82fcdbe8
queryLines:
SELECT
  Incurred_Age_Bucket,
  Gender,
  SUM(CASE 
        WHEN :claim_type = 'NH' THEN Count_NH
        WHEN :claim_type = 'ALF' THEN Count_ALF
        WHEN :claim_type = 'HHC' THEN Count_HHC
        ELSE 0
      END) / SUM(Total_Exposure) * 1000 AS Incidence_Rate
FROM
  IDENTIFIER(concat('actuarial_app_catalog.`long_term_care`.', :table_name))
WHERE
  Incurred_Age_Bucket != 'Unknown'
GROUP BY
  Incurred_Age_Bucket,
  Gender
ORDER BY
  Incurred_Age_Bucket,
  Gender

    Incurred_Age_Bucket,
    Gender,

                WHEN :variable_name IN ('Orig_Daily_Ben_Bucket', 'Ben_Period_Bucket', 'EP_Bucket')
                  THEN concat(:claim_type, '_', :variable_name)
                ELSE :variable_name
               END)),

  SELECT
  Incurred_Age_Bucket,
  Gender,
  SUM(CASE 
        WHEN :claim_type = 'NH' THEN Count_NH
        WHEN :claim_type = 'ALF' THEN Count_ALF
        WHEN :claim_type = 'HHC' THEN Count_HHC
        ELSE 0

FROM

  JOIN base_incidence b ON a.Incurred_Age_Bucket = b.Incurred_Age_Bucket

lines: Significant morbidity improvement over calendar years
For the purpose of this study, base incidence rate is set by incurred age and gender

Select the dataset and claim type for analysis:
* NH - nursing home
* ALF - alternative living facility
* HHC - home health care
This dashboard is designed to facilitate LTC incidence rate assumption setting
